#### Working in Anaconda Prompt ####

To install package: 
conda install geopandas

To install with mamba/conda forge:
mamba install -c conda-forge ipykernel

To Activate an Environment: 
conda activate -environment name-

To Do Python Scripting in Anaconda Prompt: 
python

To get out of Python Scripting:
exit()

To stop an Operation: 
ctrl + c

IF Command Prompt keeps getting stuck at Solving Environment can do this: 
conda update --all --yes

To install arcpy: 
conda install arcpy -c esri

To see list of packages in the active environment: 
conda list 

To create a new environment: 
conda create --name VSCode2




#### Troubleshooting Errors ####

# Error: OpenSSL appears to be unavailable on this machine # 
Follow these steps: https://github.com/conda/conda/issues/11982
go to location where you've install anaconda anaconda3>Library>bin. search and copy following dll files

libcrypto-1_1-x64.dll
libssl-1_1-x64.dll

and paste to anaconda3>DLLs.

then restart your pc.















